      • getResult

        public ExperimentResult getResult()
                           throws ExperimentQueryException,
                                  ExperimentDataManipulationException,
                                  ExperimentConcurrentAccessException
        Gets the current result of this experiment, which comprises all cases which at the moment of invocation can be asked for their results Produces a consolidated result file
        Returns:
        the ExperimentResult for this experiment
        Throws:
        ExperimentQueryException - if the result could not be obtained from the native system
        ExperimentDataManipulationException - if the experiment result instance to be returned could not be created due to problem trying to store the result data
        ExperimentConcurrentAccessException - if result permanent storage was being used by another instance that refers to this same experiment cases, this exception indicates another attempt should be made to get the result

      • getResult

        public ExperimentResult getResult(boolean supressResultFileGeneration)
                           throws ExperimentQueryException,
                                  ExperimentDataManipulationException,
                                  ExperimentConcurrentAccessException
        Gets the current result of this experiment, which comprises all cases which at the moment of invocation can be asked for their results
        Parameters:
        supressResultFileGeneration - true if the cases result should be obtained and - if applicable - processed but no consolidated result file should be generated, false if the consolidated result file should be produced
        Returns:
        the ExperimentResult for this experiment
        Throws:
        ExperimentQueryException - if the result could not be obtained from the native system
        ExperimentDataManipulationException - if the experiment result instance to be returned could not be created due to problem trying to store the result data
        ExperimentConcurrentAccessException - if result permanent storage was being used by another instance that refers to this same experiment cases, this exception indicates another attempt should be made to get the result

      • getAllFinishedCasesResult

        public List<ExperimentCaseResult> getAllFinishedCasesResult()
                                                     throws ExperimentQueryException,
                                                            ExperimentDataManipulationException,
                                                            ExperimentConcurrentAccessException
        Gets the results of all cases that have finished executing
        Returns:
        a List with the ExperimentCaseResult of the cases that have finished executing
        Throws:
        ExperimentQueryException - if the result could not be obtained from the native system
        ExperimentDataManipulationException - if any experiment case result instance to be returned could not be created due to problem trying to store the result data
        ExperimentConcurrentAccessException - if result permanent storage was being used by another instance that refers to this same experiment case, this exception indicates another attempt should be made to get the result
